snippet.title: Fuukan no Grasesta - Trial Version Gameplay
snippet.description:
A video of Fuukan no Grasesta's trial version reflecting some general dialogue and a boss encounter.

It was pretty anticlimactic as a matter of fact, they gave you so many healing potions as a prelude to the fight, but in the end the battle ended prematurely :/
